20pack%20up%20my%20life%20and%20book%20a%20one-way%20flight%20to%20a%20new%20city%2C%20sometimes%20even%20a%20different%20continent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20started%20in%202014%20after%20a%20brutal%20three-month%20run%3A%20a%20breakup%2C%20a%20messy%20rebound%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgot-fired-from-job-deserved-it-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egetting%20fired%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20a%20brand-new%20job.%20I%20was%20sitting%20at%20home%20in%20Johannesburg%2C%20doomscrolling%20on%20Facebook%2C%20when%20an%20email%20came%20through%20from%20an%20airline%20offering%20a%20deal%20on%20flights%20to%20Cape%20Town%2C%20South%20Africa.%20My%20interest%3F%20Piqued.%20My%20credit%20card%3F%20Ready%20to%20swipe.%20My%20impulse%20control%3F%20At%20an%20all-time%20low.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20booked%20a%20flight%20for%20the%20following%20week%20and%20immediately%20began%20boxing%20up%20my%20room%20at%20my%20mom's%20into%20three%20small%20boxes%20and%20sending%20out%20invites%20for%20farewell%20drinks%20at%20my%20favorite%20bar.%20Little%20did%20I%20know%2C%20this%20major%20life%20decision%20I%20had%20made%20in%20less%20than%2060%20seconds%20would%20go%20on%20to%20start%20a%20pattern%20of%20shaking%20up%20my%20surroundings%20to%20an%20extreme%20after%20heartbreak.%20I%20did%20it%20again%20in%202021%2C%20when%20I%20left%20Cape%20Town%20for%20Namibia%2C%20and%20last%20year%2C%20I%20said%20bon%20voyage%20to%20South%20Africa%20and%20moved%20to%20France.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20in%20Namibia%20in%20the%20sand.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6865abfa3d5881a51c1c999c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224725%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20has%20moved%20after%20every%20major%20break-up.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Lauren%20Melnick%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d993b4f1-9260-4a2a-bbcf-7640334c047f%5C%22%3EMoving%20after%20a%20break-up%20means%20I%20get%20to%20break%20old%20habits%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIs%20making%20a%20major%20move%20after%20a%20breakup%20a%20little%20dramatic%3F%20Absolutely%2C%20but%20there%20is%20a%20method%20to%20my%20madness.%20Every%20move%20forces%20me%20to%20confront%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbroke-up-with-wealthy-ex-learned-thinking-money-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epost-breakup%20identity%20crisis%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20answer%20the%20million-dollar%20question%3A%20Who%20am%20I%20without%20anyone%20else%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStarting%20over%20in%20a%20new%20place%20strips%20away%20all%20the%20relationship%20compromises%2C%20shared%20daily%20routines%2C%20and%20habits.%20The%20only%20thing%20left%20is%20me%3A%20my%20habits%2C%20my%20desires%2C%20and%20my%20identity%20beyond%20another%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20gives%20me%20the%20space%20to%20figure%20out%20where%20I%20may%20have%20been%20performing%20in%20the%20relationship%20and%20identify%20where%20I%20lost%20myself.%20The%20crisis%20I%20had%20where%20I%20wondered%20whether%20I%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchanged-mind-about-having-kids-future-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echanging%20my%20mind%20about%20having%20kids%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%20It%20turns%20out%20I%20was%20never%20unsure%20about%20having%20children%20%E2%80%94%20I%20always%20knew%20deep%20down%20that%20it%20wasn't%20my%20path.%20I%20was%20just%20too%20scared%20to%20choose%20myself%20and%20lose%20my%20partner%20in%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20my%20last%20relationship%2C%20I%20stopped%20doing%20all%20the%20things%20I%20love%3A%20DJing%2C%20hiking%2C%20and%20going%20to%20festivals.%20It%20wasn't%20until%20it%20ended%20and%20I%20moved%20yet%20again%20that%20I%20realized%20how%20much%20I'd%20been%20missing%20out%20on%20when%20I%20found%20myself%20in%20Paris%20at%20a%20rave%2C%20cheezing%20so%20hard%20my%20cheeks%20hu