20familiar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20wearing%20a%20white%20dress%20and%20sitting%20on%20a%20bridge%2C%20staring%20at%20the%20Eiffel%20Tower.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6865ac7985e81483682d484e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221125%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAfter%20moving%2C%20the%20author%20often%20realizes%20parts%20of%20herself%20she%20lost%20while%20in%20her%20relationship.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Lauren%20Melnick%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20time%20I%20moved%20after%20a%20breakup%20was%20on%20impulse.%20When%20I%20realized%20it%20was%20helping%20me%20process%20what%20had%20happened%20and%20improve%20my%20relationship%20with%20myself%2C%20I%20got%20curious%20and%20wanted%20to%20know%20why.%20I%20learned%20that%20when%20I%20create%20new%20memories%20and%20daily%20habits%2C%20I'm%20training%20my%20brain%20to%20form%20new%20associations%20that%20aren't%20tied%20to%20my%20ex.%20So%20when%20I%20move%2C%20I'm%20rewiring%20neural%20pathways%2C%20and%20I'm%20spending%20less%20energy%20stuck%20in%20a%20loop%20replaying%20the%20same%20old%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20you%20can't%20move%20cities%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feurope-trip-without-partner-prefer-solo-travel-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplan%20a%20solo%20trip%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20two%20weeks.%20You'll%20still%20get%20to%20reap%20the%20benefits%20of%20taking%20yourself%20out%20of%20the%20familiar%20and%20give%20your%20heart%20and%20brain%20the%20chance%20to%20reset%20and%20interrupt%20the%20emotional%20ties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20an%20incredible%20heartbreak%20cure%2C%20and%20reader%2C%20it's%20probably%20the%20greatest%20gift%20I've%20given%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fafter-major-break-up-move-new-city-heal-heartbreak