ng%20for%20more%20customized%20risk%20parameters%2C%20which%20the%20largest%20funds%20struggle%20to%20offer%20given%20their%20organizations'%20size.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20why%20places%20like%20New%20Holland%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-smaller-hedge-funds-are-bringing-portfolio-managers-in-house-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eamong%20other%20smaller%20funds%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20have%20decided%20to%20bring%20more%20talent%20in-house%20even%20as%20bigger%20firms%20like%20Millennium%20increasingly%20allocate%20to%20external%20managers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20trying%20to%20be%20indifferent%20%E2%80%94%20we%20want%20to%20find%20good%20talent%20and%20have%20a%20home%20for%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20New%20Holland%20CEO%20Scott%20Radke%2C%20who%20noted%20that%20he%20still%20expects%20most%20of%20the%20firm's%20investors%20to%20be%20external.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20manager%20has%20more%20than%2040%20external%20managers%20right%20now%2C%20while%20Plum%20Island%20has%20one%20internal%20PM%2C%20an%20equity%20capital%20markets%20investor.%20The%20new%20unit%20expects%20to%20add%20several%20more%20this%20year%2C%20but%20has%20no%20set%20goal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20Holland%20began%20as%20an%20investment%20advisor%20for%20Dutch%20pension%20plans%20and%20has%20since%20become%20independent.%20Last%20month%2C%20it%20hired%20former%20Brevan%20Howard%20executive%20Stephan%20Brohme%20as%20its%20chief%20risk%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-holland-new-platform-hire-internal-portfolio-managers-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1751881861000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6866c738f748d8c055f4f652%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-holland-new-platform-hire-internal-portfolio-managers-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22