0on%20its%20nuclear%20facilities%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Firan-trump-cybersecurity-hacking-9009bff8425d97366e9423b50fb52edf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIran-linked%20hackers%3C%2Fa%3E%20responded%20by%20targeting%20American%20banks%20and%20defense%20contractors%2C%20as%20well%20as%20oil%20producers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArnie%20Bellini%2C%20managing%20partner%20of%20cybersecurity%20investment%20firm%20Bellini%20Capital%2C%20believes%20that%20the%20US%20government%20will%20double%20down%20on%20cybersecurity%20%E2%80%94%20and%20he%20sees%20a%20key%20opportunity%20for%20investors%20in%20a%20handful%20of%20stocks%20that%20could%20benefit%20from%20the%20heightened%20spending.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20people%20can%20make%20lots%20of%20money%20in%20the%20cyber%20space%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20really%20smart%20play.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBellini%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20he's%20eyeing%20these%20stocks%20as%20top%20picks%20in%20the%20space.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220f8b34a5-3377-436f-9970-d09bf399d91f%5C%22%3EPalo%20Alto%20Networks%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20Bellini's%20perspective%2C%20cybersecurity%20firms%20that%20are%20strongly%20aligned%20with%20the%20federal%20government%20are%20in%20the%20best%20position%20to%20gain.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20sees%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fpanw-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPalo%20Alto%20Networks%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20best%20cybersecurity%20play%2C%20due%20to%20the%20company's%20federal%20alignment%2C%20dynamic%20list%20of%20product%20and%20artificial%20intelligence%20(AI)%20integration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey've%20already%20worked%20with%20the%20government%20agencies%2C%20and%20they're%20rapidly%20expanding%20AI%20integrated%20threat%20detection%20and%20zero%20trust%20architecture%20to%20modern%2C%20very%20appropriate%20approaches%20to%2