20in%20the%20new%20market%20for%20injectable%20diabetes%20and%20weight%20loss%20medications.%20But%20ever%20since%202022%2C%20when%20Eli%20Lilly's%20tirzepatide%20was%20first%20approved%20for%20use%20in%20the%20US%2C%20Lilly's%20been%20steadily%20gaining%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20company%20is%20developing%20a%20menu%20of%20other%20obesity%20drugs%20that%20could%20cater%20to%20anyone.%20There's%20a%20pill%20for%20weight%20loss%20instead%20of%20an%20injection.%20There%20are%20drugs%20that%20tap%20into%20new%20appetite-regulating%20hormones%3B%20an%20antibody%20injection%20to%20protect%20muscles%20while%20burning%20up%20excess%20fat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInvestors%20are%20starting%20to%20talk%20about%20Lilly%20on%20their%20own%20cue%2C%20rather%20than%20in%20the%20context%20of%20Novo%2C%26quot%3B%20Asad%20Haider%2C%20Goldman%20Sachs's%20lead%20analyst%20for%20US%20pharmaceuticals%2C%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20almost%20every%20existing%20as%20well%20as%20emerging%20mechanism%20across%20anti-obesity%2C%20and%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20really%20hard%2C%20in%20our%20view%2C%20to%20leapfrog%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20we%20caught%20up%20with%20Eli%20Lilly%20Executive%20Vice%20President%20Ken%20Custer%2C%20the%20man%20overseeing%20it%20all.%20Custer%20is%20the%20new%20president%20of%20Lilly's%20cardiometabolic%20health%20division%2C%20and%20in%20a%20recent%20one-on-one%20with%20BI%2C%20he%20shared%20the%20strategy%20behind%20the%20company's%20success%20so%20far%20and%20how%20they%20plan%20to%20maintain%20their%20big%20lead%20in%20the%20long%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225d5d7aca-042b-418e-b1f5-d0c4e61a0103%5C%22%3EEli%20Lilly%20is%20set%20to%20dominate%20the%20market%20by%202030%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22tirzepatide%20pen%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6866d12a85e81483682d5fca%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223871%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETirzepatide%20is%20marketed%20for%20diabetes%20as%20Mounjaro%20and%20for%20obesity%20as%20Zepbound.%3Cp%3EPeter%20Dazeley%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEli%20Lilly's%20tirzepatide%2C%20the%20drug%20currently%20leading%20the%20charge%2C%20is%20the%20strongest%20weight%20loss%20drug%20available%20so%20far.%20While%20Novo's%20Wegovy%20supercharges%20one%20of%20our%20hunger%20hormones%20(GLP-1)%2C%20Lilly's%20Mounjaro%20has%20two%20(GLP-1%20and%20GIP)%2C%20making%20it%20a%20more%20powerful%20weekly%20shot%20to%20control%20appetite%20and%20blood%20sugar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20recent%20head-to-head%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjamanetwork.com%2Fjournals%2Fjamainternalmedicine%2Ffullarticle%2F2821080%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudy%3C%2Fa%3E%20showed%20patients%20who%20spent%20a%20year%20on%20tirzepatide%20lost%2C%20on%20average%2C%20about%2015%25%20of%20their%20body%20weight%2C%20while%20those%20on%20semaglutide%20(the%20drug%20in%20Ozempic)%20lost%20just%208%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%202030%2C%20Goldman%20is%20forecasting%2C%20conservatively%2C%20that%20Lilly%20will%20capture%20nearly%2050%25%20of%20the%20%2495%20billion%20anti-obesity%20medicine%20market.%20That%20forecast%20includes%20the%20injectable%20drugs%20we%20have%20now%2C%20like%20Mounjaro%20and%20Ozempic%20(for%20diabetes)%20plus%20Wegovy%20and%20Zepbound%20(for%20obesity)%20but%20may%20also%20extend%20to%20new%20drugs%20in%20the%20pipeline%2C%20both%20at%20Eli%20Lilly%20and%20coming%20from%20other%20drugmakers%20with%20smaller%20portfolios.%20But%20right%20now%2C%20Lilly%20seems%20to%20be%20ahead%20of%20the%20competition%20in%20just%20about%20every%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20June%2C%20at%20the%20American%20Diabetes%20Association's%20big%20annual%20research%20conference%20(ADA)%2C%20Lilly's%20updates%20from%20ongoing%20trials%20were%20%26quot%3Bincrementally%20better%26quot%3B%20than%20investors%20had%20expected%2C%20Haider%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThen%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20that%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20their%20late-stage%20competition%20%E2%80%94%20specifically%20Novo%20Nordisk%2C%20but%20also%20Amgen%20%E2%80%94%20the%20updates%20that%20you%20got%20from%20them%20at%20ADA%20had%20a%20little%20bit%20more%20hair%20on%20them%2C%20and%20were%20frankly%20met%20with%20more%20disappointment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22055af17a-8043-437c-823e-cecd649c9e79%5C%22%3E1.%20Speed%3A%20'This%20ratchet%20mindset'%20drives%20Lilly%20to%20develop%20drugs%20faster%20and%20faster%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221674%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Eli%20Lilly%20CEO%20Dave%20Ricks%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6866d0463d5881a51c1cb108%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222510%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEli%20Lilly%20CEO%20Dave%20Ricks%20has%20led%20the%20company%20since%202017.%3Cp%3EEli%20Lilly%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEli%20Lilly%20CEO%20Dave%20Ricks%20shared%20some%20of%20the%20secrets%20behind%20the%20big%20speed%20up%20that's%20shifted%20the%20company%20from%20an%2011-year%20average%20time%20to%20market%20(when%20he%20first%20became%20CEO%20in%202017)%20to%20a%20six-year%20average%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20really%20track%20things%20very%20carefully%20on%20speed%2C%26quot%3B%20Ricks%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20last%20October%20on%20the%20%26quot%3BAll-In%26quot%3B%20podcast.%20%26quot%3BThe%20big%20idea%20is%20like%20this%20ratchet%20mindset%20that%20every%20time%20we%20beat%20a%20timeline%2C%20that%20becomes%20the%20new%20norm.%20We%20just%20re-benchmark%20internally.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECase%20in%20point%3A%20It%20took%20about%20two%20decades%20to%20get%20Trulicity%2C%20Eli%20Lilly's%20first%20GLP-1%20drug%2C%20on%20the%20market.%20Tirzepatide%3F%20About%20eight%20years%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3Bblistering%20speed%2C%26quot%3B%20Custer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22249317b9-ba3a-4db5-9942-e42fd1702606%5C%22%3E2.%20Convenience%3A%20a%20cheap(er)%20pill%20to%20rival%20Ozempic%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20pill%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62ff683fec781d001868cdeb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEli%20Lilly%20is%20already%20manufacturing%20its%20Ozempic-like%20pill%20(not%20pictured)%20even%20though%20the%20FDA%20hasn't%20yet%20approved%20the%20drug%2C%20called%20orforglipron.%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEli%20Lilly%20is%20in%20the%20late%20stages%20of%20developing%20the%20first%20Ozempic-like%20pill%2C%20designed%20to%20be%20just%20as%20strong%20as%20Novo's%20injectable%20drug.%20The%20drug%2C%20orforglipron%2C%20could%20be%20available%20as%20early%20as%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20only%20about%208%20million%20people%20currently%20on%20Mounjaro%2C%20Ozempic%2C%20Wegovy%2C%20and%20Zepbound%20in%20the%20US%2C%20which%20speaks%20to%20both%20the%20high%20cost%20of%20the%20injectable%20drugs%20and%20the%20supply%20bottlenecks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20injectable%20GLP-1s%20are%20wonderful%20medicines%2C%20but%20manufacturing%20those%20medicines%20is%20hard%2C%26quot%3B%20Custer%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20factories%20that%20you%20have%20to%20use%20to%20do%20the%20sterile%20filling%20of%20the%20vials%2C%20the%20syringes%2C%20the%20devices%2C%20the%20cartridges%20are%20extraordinarily%20hard%20to%20build%20and%20operate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECuster%20believes%20a%20daily%20pill%20could%20completely%20change%20the%20game%20%E2%80%94%20opening%20up%20this%20new%20class%20of%20hormone-mimicking%20weight%20loss%20and%20diabetes%20drugs%20called%20incretins%20to%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20more%20people%20across%20the%20globe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20we're%20at%20a%20defining%20moment%20in%20our%20company's%20history%2C%26quot%3B%20Custer%20said.%20He%20added%20that%20he%20sees%20this%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20generational%20opportunity%20that%20is%20probably%20close%20to%20what%20was%20seen%20with%20the%20early%20days%20of%20vaccines%20and%20antibiotics.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEli%20Lilly%20is%20already%20manufacturing%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20orforglipron%20pills%2C%20just%20to%20make%20sure%20it%20will%20be%20able%20to%20meet%20the%20demand%20if%20the%20drug%20is%20approved%20for%20use%20in%20the%20US%20next%20year.%20That's%20a%20somewhat%20risky%20move%2C%20considering%20that%20the%20company's%20final%20Phase%203%20clinical%20trials%20that%20the%20US%20Food%20and%20Drug%20administration%20requires%20to%20evaluate%20the%20drug%20aren't%20even%20done%20yet.%20If%20approved%2C%20orforglipron%20should%20also%20(thankfully)%20have%20a%20more%20pronounceable%20brand%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExpect%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20pill%20to%20rival%20a%20%26quot%3Bfancy%20gym%20membership%2C%26quot%3B%20Shin%20said%2C%20meaning%20maybe%20around%20%24300%20for%20one%20month%20%E2%80%94%20a%20quarter%20of%20the%20cost%20of%20some%20injectable%20weight-loss%20drugs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20companies'%20attempts%20to%20develop%20a%20new%20weight%20loss%20pill%20have%20been%20lackluster.%20Pfizer%20ditched%20its%20obesity%20pill%20candidate%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20while%20Novo%20Nordisk's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fozempic-pills-coming-but-may-not-be-convenient-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epill%20version%20of%20semaglutide%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20called%20Rybelsus%2C%20is%20not%20nearly%20as%20effective%20as%20Ozempic%3A%20Most%20patients%20on%20the%20pill%20lose%20less%20than%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Farticles%2FPMC8206300%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E5%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20their%20body%20weight%2C%20while%20people%20using%20the%20weekly%20shot%20can%20often%20achieve%2010-15%25%20weight%20loss%2C%20or%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22055ffeec-0e50-40e7-9ddd-1a207d1b4dcc%5C%22%3E3.%20Creating%20a%20laundry%20list%20of%20new%20options%20to%20get%20ahead%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222100%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22iv%20drip%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6866d20d3d5881a51c1cb185%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221401%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELilly's%20muscle-preserving%20drug%2C%20bimagrumab%20(not%20pictured)%20is%20delivered%20intravenously.%3Cp%3ESergii%20Kolesnikov%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20north%20star%20of%20Eli%20Lilly's%20strategy%20now%20is%20variety%20%E2%80%94%20developing%20a%20broader%20range%20of%20options%20for%20consumers%20than%20any%20of%20their%20competitors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20have%20a%20billion%20people%20around%20the%20world%20or%20more%20living%20with%20overweight%20or%20obesity%2C%20they're%20not%20all%20going%20to%20be%20helped%20by%20one%20medicine%2C%26quot%3B%20Custer%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20see%20this%20segmenting%20it%20into%20several%20logical%20categories.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shift%20is%20already%20underway%20to%20find%20new%20weight%20loss%20options%20that%20will%20harness%20different%20hunger%20hormones%20(like%20amylin)%2C%20use%20new%20routes%20of%20administration%20(pills%20or%20IVs%20instead%20of%20just%20injection%20pens)%2C%20and%20have%20different%20dosing%20schedules%20(daily%2C%20weekly%2C%20or%20monthly).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20trying%20to%20address%20every%20type%20of%20patient%2C%26quot%3B%20Shin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20the%20menu%2C%20beyond%20orforglipron%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBimagrumab%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ELooking%20to%20protect%20muscle%20while%20you%20lose%20fat%3F%20This%20is%20an%20Eli%20Lilly%20drug%20which%20may%20become%20available%20after%20orforglipron%2C%20if%20the%20mid-stage%20trials%20go%20well%20in%20the%20next%20couple%20of%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20most%20recent%20trial%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdiabetes.org%2Fnewsroom%2Fpress-releases%2Fnew-glp-1-therapies-enhance-quality-weight-loss-improving-muscle-0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresults%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20company%20shared%20on%20bimagrumab%20at%20ADA%2C%20patients%20on%20the%20drug%20achieved%20100%25%20fat%20loss%2C%20essentially%20preserving%20all%20their%20muscles.%20This%20idea%20of%20making%20sure%20patients%20lose%20the%20right%20kind%20of%20weight%20%E2%80%94%20not%20compromising%20their%20strength%20just%20to%20slim%20down%20%E2%80%94%20is%20the%20holy%20grail%20in%20incretin%20drug%20development%20right%20now%2C%20generating%20tons%20of%20buzz%20and%20investment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221439%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22King%20Kong%201933%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F599b72964dcf353e008b4b33%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEli%20Lilly's%20investigational%20drug%20retatrutide%20has%20been%20dubbed%20the%20%26quot%3Bking%20kong%26quot%3B%20for%20weight%20loss%2C%20because%20it%20is%20more%20powerful%20than%20anything%20on%20the%20market%20today.%3Cp%3ERKO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretatrutide-patients-lose-more-weight-than-ozempic-wegovy-mounjaro-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ERetatrutide%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIf%20it's%20more%20powerful%20drugs%20you're%20after%2C%20then%20there's%20the%20%26quot%3Bking%20kong%26quot%3B%20triple%20agonist%20that%20the%20company%20has%20been%20working%20on.%20It%20won't%20likely%20be%20ready%20to%20approve%20until%20late%202026%2C%20at%20the%20very%20earliest%2C%20but%20in%20clinical%20trials%2C%20it%20has%20shown%20weight%20loss%20on%20par%20with%20bariatric%20surgery%2C%20and%20some%20patients%20have%20lost%20more%20than%20a%20third%20of%20their%20total%20body%20weight%2C%20requiring%20entirely%20new%20wardrobes.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EEloralintide%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EFinally%2C%20there's%20Lilly's%20investigational%20drug%20that%20mimics%20amylin%2C%20another%20metabolism-regulating%20hormone.%20It's%20still%20early%20days%20for%20eloralintide%20and%20for%20amylin%20medications%20in%20general.%20So%20it's%20possible%20that%20competitors%20like%20Novo%20Nordisk%20or%20Amgen%20could%20develop%20a%20compelling%20amylin%20drug%20before%20Eli%20Lilly%20does.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat's%20exciting%20is%20we%20feel%20like%20we're%20leading%20in%20most%2C%20if%20not%20all%20of%20those%20categories%2C%20but%20we'll%20come%20up%20with%20new%20categories%2C%26quot%3B%20Custer%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20really%20about%20tailoring.%20I%20think%20bimagrumab%20and%20eloralintide%20and%20retatrutide%20and%20orforglipron%20are%20really%20the%20first%20part%20of%20that%20story%2C%20but%20of%20course%2C%20we%20have%20other%20ideas%20we're%20working%20on%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20want%20in%20on%20that%20action.%20Both%20Goldman%20Sachs%20and%20Deutsche%20Bank%20sent%20BI%20disclosure%20statements%20for%20this%20story%2C%20because%20they%20each%20have%20a%20financial%20relationship%20with%20Eli%20Lilly%20(I%20challenge%20you%2C%20dear%20reader%2C%20to%20find%20a%20major%20investment%20bank%20that%20does%20not).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20long%20run%2C%20Eli%20Lilly%20is%20thinking%20ahead%20to%20a%20day%20when%20this%20class%20of%20medications%20could%20even%20treat%20conditions%20beyond%20metabolism%20and%20heart%20health%2C%20including%20dementia%2C%20inflammation%2C%20substance%20abuse%2C%20and%20pain.%20(Scientists%20are%20starting%20to%20study%20whether%20incretin%20drugs%20might%20treat%20migraines%2C%20for%20example).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20may%20be%20even%20in%20the%20future%2C%20when%20you're%20checking%20out%20at%20Kroger%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20'get%20your%20annual%20flu%20vaccine%2C'%20you%20see%20a%20sign%20that%20says%20'get%20your%20annual%20metabolic%20shot%2C'%26quot%3B%20Custer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feli-lilly-3-step-strategy-dominate-95-billion-obesity-market-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1751880601000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6866dea485e81483682d627c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feli-lilly-3-step-strategy-dominate-95-billion-obesity-market-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Business%20Insider%20spoke%20to%20Eli%20Lilly's%20new%20president%20of%20cardiometabolic%20health%2C%20who%20shared%20the%20company's%20aggressive%20incretin%20drug%20strategy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22hbrueck%40businessinsider.com%20(Hilary%20Brueck)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feli-lilly-3-step-strategy-dominate-95-billion-obesity-market-2025-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22King%3A%20SRK%2C%20Suhana%20to%20begin%20European%20schedule%20in%20August%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1751880560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-122295407%2Cimgsize-50084.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fshah-rukh-khan-suhana-khan-and-abhishek-bachchan-take-a-break-from-king-shoot-to-commence-action-packed-european-schedule-in-august%2Farticleshow%2F122294354.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F122294354.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EAfter%20an%20intense%20initial%20schedule%20at%20Mehboob%20Studios%2