ss%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20the%20J.%20Thelander%20Consulting%20report%20focused%20on%20smaller%20firms%2C%20some%20Big%20Tech%20companies%20have%20also%20recently%20made%20headlines%20for%20their%20sky-high%20recruitment%20incentives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20was%20in%20the%20spotlight%20last%20month%20after%20Sam%20Altman%2C%20CEO%20of%20OpenAI%2C%20said%20the%20social%20media%20giant%20had%20tried%20to%20poach%20his%20best%20employees%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-sam-altman-countered-meta-signing-bonuses-ai-talent-war-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%24100%20million%20signing%20bonuses%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Business%20Insider%20previously%20reported%20that%20Altman%20later%20quipped%20that%20none%20of%20his%20%26quot%3Bbest%20people%26quot%3B%20had%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-meta-tried-poaching-openai-staff-ai-talent-war-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eenticed%20by%20the%20deal%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20Meta's%20chief%20technology%20officer%2C%20Andrew%20Bosworth%2C%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20CNBC%20that%20Altman%20%26quot%3Bneglected%20to%20mention%20that%20he's%20countering%20those%20offers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-companies-recruit-pay-bonuses-higher-salaries-ai-experience-report-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1751879702000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6865d1f785e81483682d49ae%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-companies-recruit-pay-bonuses-higher-salaries-ai-experience-report-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20consulting%20firm%20found%20that%20tech%20companies%20are%20%26quot%3Bstrategically%20overpaying%26quot%3B%20recruits%20with%20AI%20experience%2C%20paying%20premiums%20of%20%24200%2C00