%3Cp%3EThese%20conversations%20in%20my%20work%20and%20my%20own%20life%20have%20given%20me%20a%20unique%20perspective%20on%20how%20to%20get%20started%20and%20stay%20committed.%20It%20helps%20my%20clients%20to%20have%20someone%20they%20can%20trust%20with%20their%20sensitive%20information%20who%20also%20%26quot%3Bgets%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESaving%20and%20investing%20for%20our%20kids%20was%20not%20instant%20or%20overnight%3B%20it's%20taken%20years%20of%20learning%20and%20contributing.%20First%2C%20we%20had%20to%20make%20sure%20our%20own%20retirement%20and%20savings%20were%20healthily%20funded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20how%20I%20set%20up%20my%20kids%20for%20financial%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2240c9cf76-5ec1-4157-8b59-c8b19a1be1a3%5C%22%3EI%20started%20529s%20for%20each%20of%20my%20two%20kids%20when%20they%20were%20born%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarted-529-college-plan-son-money-tight-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E529s%20are%20special%20accounts%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20allow%20you%20to%20save%20tax-free%20for%20education%20expenses.%20My%20parents%20did%20the%20same%20for%20me%20before%20I%20was%20college-age.%20Not%20needing%20to%20worry%20about%20finances%2C%20loans%2C%20and%20tuition%20made%20it%20much%20easier%20for%20me%20to%20focus%20on%20my%20studies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20set%20up%20these%20accounts%20because%20we%20want%20our%20kids%20to%20have%20flexibility.%20I%20want%20them%20to%20be%20able%20to%20comfortably%20search%20for%20their%20ideal%20job%20fit%20since%20they%20already%20have%20a%20savings%20cushion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20have%20saved%20over%20%24100%2C000%20in%20each%20of%20their%20529s.%20I%20fund%20their%20accounts%20so%20that%20they'll%20be%20similarly%20situated%20based%20on%20the%20year%20they%20attend%20college.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20state%20has%20its%20own%20529%20providers.%20I%20decided%20to%20use%20California's%20plan%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scholarshare529.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EScholar%20Share%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20it%20was%20easy%20to%20set%20up.%20I%20want%20to%20save%20100%25%20of%20what%20is%20expected%20for%20a%20public%20university%20in%20California.%20The%20target%20goal%20for%20each%20of%20the%20529s%20is%20%24200%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20don't%20have%20a%20specific%20backup%20plan%20for%20the%20money%20if%20one%20of%20the%20kids%20doesn't%20attend%20college%2C%20but%20up%20to%20%2435%2C000%20can%20be%20diverted%20to%20a%20Roth%20IRA.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20funds%20can%20still%20be%20withdrawn%20(with%20a%20penalty%20on%20earnings)%2C%20which%20is%20not%20an%20issue%20for%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20could%20also%20change%20the%20beneficiary%20to%20a%20different%20family%20member%20(e.g.%2C%20hypothetical%20grandchild).%20I'd%20rather%20be%20over-prepared%20financially%20than%20under-prepared%20and%20have%20to%20scramble%20to%20figure%20things%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2251824b76-43da-4934-9f78-d2fa41e17364%5C%22%3EI%20also%20set%20up%20custodial%20Roth%20IRAs%20for%20them%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Froth-ira-for-kids%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECustodial%20Roth%20IRAs%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20retirement%20accounts%20in%20which%20a%20child%20can%20deposit%20earnings%20from%20a%20job%20while%20they're%20minors%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20start%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fretirement-planning%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eretirement%20savings%3C%2Fa%3E%20early.%20I've%20saved%20five%20figures%20in%20each%20of%20their%20custodial%20Roth%20IRAs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20business%20owners%2C%20there%20are%20ways%20to%20employ%20your%20kids%20to%20set%20up%20a%20Roth%20IRA%20legally.%20Now%20that%20my%20kids%20are%2010%20and%208%2C%20they've%20been%20able%20to%20help%20me%20with%20shredding%20paperwork%20and%20other%20small%20tasks.%20They%20know%20that%20they're%20earning%20money%20for%20the%20work%20that%20they%20contribute%20to%20my%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnyone%20can%20set%20up%20a%20529%20for%20their%20loved%20ones%2C%20but%20custodial%20Roth%20IRAs%20are%20only%20available%20if%20a%20child%20has%20earned%20income.%20If%20someone%20is%20not%20a%20business%20owner%20and%20their%20child%20is%20old%20enough%2C%20the%20child%20can%20work%20and%20still%20have%20a%20custodial%20Roth%20IRA.%20The%20work%20can%20be%20with%20an%20established%20business%2C%20or%20even%20helping%20others%20in%20the%20community%20with%20babysitting%20and%20other%20chores.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228fb8fbe5-d9ce-4ce3-a2d4-d4c28f6c5faf%5C%22%3EThey%20also%20have%20their%20own%20bank%20accounts%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20UTMA%20bank%20accounts%20are%20kept%20leaner%2C%20in%20the%20hundreds%20of%20dollars.%20UTMA%20bank%20accounts%20hold%20money%20that%20your%20child%20owns%2C%20and%20an%20adult%20is%20the%20custodian%20until%20the%20child%20becomes%20an%20adult.%20A%20portion%20of%20birthday%20money%20or%20gifts%20goes%20into%20the%20UTMA%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBirthday%20and%20Christmas%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fholiday-gift-giving-strategy-good-money-habits-parents-children-advice-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egifts%20in%20cash%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20typically%20from%20grandparents%20or%20other%20family%20members.%20Because%20these%20gifts%20are%20not%20earned%20income%2C%20the%20%26quot%3Bsave%26quot%3B%20goes%20to%20UTMA%20accounts%20and%20not%20to%20their%20Roth%20IRAs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20have%20a%20set%20savings%20strategy.%20I%20add%20funds%20when%20I%20have%20more%20money%20in%20my%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2292e238c3-0bfa-4893-a197-612035c50c2f%5C%22%3EThere%20are%202%20things%20I%20could've%20done%20differently%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20could%20do%20better%20at%20automating%20a%20monthly%20amount%20to%20ensure%20consistency%20and%20streamline%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20thing%20I%20could've%20done%20differently%20is%20deeper%20research%20into%20529%20providers.%20I'm%20OK%20with%20our%20California%20provider%2C%20but%20researching%20more%20couldn't%20hurt.%20529s%20can%20have%20differences%2C%20such%20as%20the%20types%20of%20investments%20available%2C%20the%20funds%20set%20up%2C%20the%20minimum%20amount%20required%20to%20get%20started%2C%20or%20the%20maintenance%20fees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tell%20my%20clients%20it's%20a%20good%20idea%20to%20teach%20financial%20acumen%20at%20a%20young%20age%20so%20their%20children%20don't%20spend%20their%20savings%20inappropriately.%20Our%20kids%20know%20how%20much%20is%20in%20their%20retirement%20accounts%20because%20I%20want%20them%20to%20learn%20cause%20and%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20used%20to%20get%20annoyed%20about%20helping%20me%20with%20the%20administrative%20tasks%2C%20but%20since%20I've%20educated%20them%2C%20they%20understand%20these%20funds%20will%20help%20alleviate%20stress%20when%20they%20enter%20the%20job%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2220d5607b-d8bb-4d33-95f5-dbe611d2ac7c%5C%22%3EMy%20advice%20to%20parents%20is%20to%20see%20this%20as%20a%20long%20game%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20will%20be%20dips%2C%20and%20people%20need%20to%20understand%20the%20time%20value%20of%20money%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fcagr%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecompounding%3C%2Fa%3E.%20If%20they%20move%20things%20around%20or%20make%20big%20shifts%20every%20time%20there's%20a%20decline%20in%20the%20market%2C%20it%20could%20be%20counterproductive%20and%20go%20against%20their%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20529s%2C%20I've%20taken%20a%20more%20passive%20approach%20and%20use%20age-based%20funds%20(enrollment-year%20portfolios)%20rather%20than%20risk-based%20portfolios%20or%20guaranteed%20investment%20options.%20I%20have%20not%20changed%20the%20fund%20allocations%20during%20market%20shifts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20just%20getting%20started%20or%20aren't%20in%20a%20position%20to%20make%20big%20contributions%2C%20saving%20even%20a%20few%20dollars%20a%20week%20or%20a%20month%20is%20better%20than%20nothing.%20It%20makes%20a%20difference.%20It's%20especially%20helpful%20if%20your%20children%20are%20young%20and%20time%20is%20on%20your%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-saved-6-figures-2-children-college-529-plan-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1751879101000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68657595f748d8c055f4d84a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-saved-6-figures-2-children-college-529-plan-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shannon%20Liu%20Shair%20started%20529s%20for%20each%20of%20her%20two%20kids%20when%20they%20were%20born%20and%20both%20accounts%20have%20grown%20to%20%24100%2C000.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Kaila%20Yu)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-saved-6-figures-2-children-college-529-plan-2025-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22AI%20is%20shaking%20up%20Hollywood.%20Here%20are%20the%20startups%20and%20investors%20jumping%20into%20the%20fray.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22BCS%20601%2C%20Better%20Call%20Saul%2C%20Lalo%20Salamanca%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F625dafa83958c2001823eff2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAMC%20Networks'%20%26quot%3BBetter%20Call%20Saul.%26quot%3B%20The%20company%20recently%20did%20a%20deal%20with%20Runway%20to%20use%20its%20AI%20for%20marketing.%3Cp%3EGreg%20Lewis%2FSony%20Pictures%20Television%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EHollywood%20companies%20continue%20to%20integrate%20AI%2C%20even%20as%20they%20challenge%20its%20applications%20in%20court.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAI%20startups%20like%20Toonstar%20and%20Chronicle%20Studios%20are%20innovating%20in%20animation.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EStudios%20are%20using%20the%20tech%20to%20promote%20content%20discovery%20and%20reduce%20production%20costs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EHollywood%20giants%20are%20pushing%20back%20on%20AI's%20encroachment.%20Disney%20and%20Universal%20recently%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-universal-midjourney-images-evidence-copyright-infringement-lawsuit-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esued%20Midjourney%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20accusing%20it%20of%20using%20tech%20to%20rip%20off%20their%20famous%20characters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20inside%20entertainment%20companies%2C%20it's%20a%20whole%20different%20story.%20The%20biggest%20studios%20and%20filmmakers%20are%20using%20AI%20technology%20in%20various%20ways%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20people%20in%20Hollywood%20are%20taking%20note.%20The%20AI%20on%20the%20Lot%20conference%20in%20May%20has%20doubled%20its%20attendance%20to%201%2C200%20over%20three%20years%2C%20while%20AI%20editing%20company%20Runway%20attracted%20some%201%2C000%20people%20to%20its%20third%20film%20festival.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tantalizing%20promise%20of%20AI%20is%20that%20it%20could%20solve%20big%20problems%20in%20the%20entertainment%20business%2C%20like%20content%20discovery%20and%20high%20production%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20matter%20how%20you%20feel%20about%20AI%20tools%20in%20the%20media%20and%20entertainment%20business%2C%20they're%20here%20to%20stay%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Peter%20Csathy%2C%20who%20advises%20media%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20are%20climbing%20on%20board%20companies%20like%20Ecco%2C%20an%20AI%20startup%20that%20helps%20people%20find%20titles%20across%20multiple%20streamers%20using%20queries%20like%20%26quot%3Bfind%20me%20all%20the%20shows%20about%20F1.%26quot%3B%20It%20has%20raised%20%247%20million%20from%20Ben%20Silverman%2C%20Shaquille%20O'Neal%2C%20and%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20such%20investor%20is%20Ishan%20Sinha%2C%20a%20consumer%20partner%20at%20Point72%20Ventures.%20He%20said%20the%20hype%20around%20AI-generated%20video%20hasn't%20translated%20into%20consumer%20interest.%20He%20sees%20the%20most%20potential%20in%20companies%20that%20use%20AI%20to%20promote%20distribution%20through%20personalization%2C%20translation%2C%20and%20IP%20ownership.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20the%20winning%20consumer%20businesses%20aggregate%20eyeballs%20%E2%80%94%20they%20have%20some%20type%20of%20a%20hook%2C%20whether%20it's%20content%20aggregation%2C%20playlists%2C%20proprietary%20IP%2C%20etc.%2C%20that%20acquires%20and%20retains%20users%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPoint72%20Ventures'%20investments%20include%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fglobalcomix.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGlobalComix%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20uses%20AI%20to%20bring%20recommendations%20and%20language%20translation%20to%20comic%20book%20and%20manga%20readers%20that%20they%20couldn't%20otherwise%20find%2C%20and%20Cheehoo%2C%20which%20is%20working%20with%20studios%20to%20simplify%20animation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20also%20invested%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fex-dreamworks-president-raises-millions-chronicle-ai-franchises-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChronicle%20Studios%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20aims%20to%20help%20animators%20grow%20their%20audiences%20and%20monetize%20their%20projects%20beyond%20YouTube.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20some%20AI%20companies%20transforming%20different%20areas%20of%20Hollywood%2C%20and%20the%20pitch%20decks%20some%20of%20them%20used%20to%20raise%20funding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228f15d070-96a6-4c18-85e6-f2a234dc1eea%5C%22%3EFaster