ong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIncreasing%20our%20employees'%20AI%20fluency%20is%20a%20strategic%20priority.%20They%20get%20AI%20training%20from%20the%20day%20they%20start%20at%20Carlyle%2C%20and%20are%20introduced%20to%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20tools%20they%20can%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%2090%25%20of%20our%20employees%20use%20tools%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-named-chatgpt-in-a-late-night-decision-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EChatGPT%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20Perplexity%2C%20and%20Copilot.%20We%20also%20have%20an%20AI%20champions'%20council%20where%20early%20adopters%20can%20play%20around%20with%20tools%20and%20eventually%20share%20best%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20using%20AI%20to%20transform%20our%20workflows%20through%20Project%20Catalyst%2C%20which%20automates%20processes.%20We're%20also%20developing%20custom%20tools%20that%20leverage%20proprietary%20data%20to%20deliver%20insights%20instantly%E2%80%94saving%20investors%20from%20sifting%20through%20endless%20materials.%20Today%2C%20Carlyle's%20credit%20investors%20can%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-speeding-up-fundamental-investing-jpmorgan-alliance-bernstein-blackrock-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eassess%20a%20company%20in%20hours%3C%2Fa%3E%20using%20generative%20AI%2C%20instead%20of%20spending%20weeks%20on%20research.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20is%20AI%20impacting%20the%20average%20worker%20at%20Carlyle%3F%20Are%20they%20required%20to%20use%20the%20technology%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20depends.%20Some%20business%20leaders%20have%20made%20it%20a%20requirement%20to%20put%20all%20investment%20committee%20memos%20in%20an%20AI%20tool%20for%20them%20to%20review.%20Others%20are%20not%20so%20direct%20about%20it%2C%20but%20everybody%20is%20seeing%20how%20it%20can%20make%20their%20jobs%20easier%20and%20challenging%20their%20teams%20in%20meetings%20to%20talk%20about%20the%20value%20they%20are%20deriving%20from