0advertorial.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20additive%20because%20you're%20helping%20users%20figure%20out%20the%20next%20question%20they%20need%20to%20ask%20to%20make%20a%20better%20decision%20or%20figure%20out%20what%20they're%20trying%20to%20do%20versus%20just%20trying%20to%20put%20something%20in%20your%20face%2C%26quot%3B%20Foutty%20said%2C%20adding%20that%2040%25%20of%20its%20users%20click%20on%20related%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerplexity%20advertisers%20pay%20on%20a%20CPM%2C%20or%20cost%20to%20reach%20a%20thousand%20impressions%2C%20model.%20A%20Perplexity%20spokesperson%20said%20advertising%20currently%20comprises%20less%20than%20a%20tenth%20of%20a%20percent%20of%20the%20company's%20total%20revenue%2C%20and%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20company's%20current%20ad%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20weeks%2C%20Perplexity%20has%20also%20introduced%20a%20perks%20program%2C%20where%20it%20provides%20subscribers%20to%20its%20Perplexity%20Pro%20service%20with%20offers%20and%20discounts%20from%20brands%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Ftaxes%2Fturbotax-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETurbotax%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20smart%20ring%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foura-ring-fitness-tracker-pros-cons-after-years-wearing-style-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOura%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20hotel%20booking%20service%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffacebook-investor-selfbook-pitch-deck-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESelfbook%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20Perplexity%20ads%20and%20perks%20are%20only%20active%20in%20the%20US.%20Foutty%20said%20the%20company%20was%20also%20considering%20more%20ways%20to%20monetize%20Perplexity's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-chatbots-christmas-shopping-weird-gifts-buying-retail-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eshopping%3C%2Fa%3E%20a