ng%20agency%20Jellyfish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20see%20strong%20adoption%20by%20users%2C%26quot%3B%20Hoover%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20rarely%20click%20out%20of%20'regular'%20AI%20results%3B%20I%20don't%20see%20them%20being%20eager%20to%20click%20on%20sponsored%20ones.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d2240fa8-9c4b-4076-9f75-b34fe41b4e4a%5C%22%3EPerplexity%20wants%20to%20build%20'long-term%20incentive'%20deals%20with%20publishers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPerplexity%20shares%20a%20portion%20of%20its%20ad%20revenue%20with%20the%20publisher%20partners%20it%20uses%20to%20help%20source%20its%20answers%2C%20which%20include%20Time%2C%20Fortune%2C%20and%20Der%20Spiegel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20doesn't%20cut%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnextdoor-ceo-cut-licensing-deals-ai-companies-llm-training-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eup-front%20licensing%20deals%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20these%20publishers%20because%20it%20isn't%20building%20foundational%20large%20language%20models%20that%20require%20content%20for%20training%2C%20Foutty%20said.%20It%20does%20offer%20these%20partners%20access%20to%20its%20enterprise%20product%20and%20APIs%20that%20can%20help%20publishers%20embed%20Perplexity's%20tech%2C%20like%20conversational%20search%2C%20into%20their%20own%20sites.%20(Disclosure%3A%20Business%20Insider's%20parent%20company%2C%20Axel%20Springer%2C%20has%20a%20multi-year%20content%20licensing%20deal%20with%20Perplexity%20rival%20OpenAI.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20model%20that%20we're%20creating%20on%20the%20revenue%20share%20side%20is%20a%20long-term%20incentive%2C%26quot%3B%20Foutty%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20a%20one-and-done.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20whether%20any%20publishers%20were%20making%20serious%20money%20from%20the%20program%2C%20Foutty%20said%20it%20was%20still%20early%20days.%20The%20publisher%20program%20launched%20in%20June%20of%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're