0IPO%20to%20be%20the%20kind%20of%20accelerator%20we're%20looking%20for%2C%26quot%3B%20Bento%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20or%20not%20startups%20decide%20to%20take%20the%20plunge%20this%20year%2C%20though%2C%20Barclays'%20head%20of%20Americas%20equity%20capital%20markets%20Rob%20Stowe%20told%20BI%20in%20June%20that%20Hinge%20Health's%20and%20Omada%20Health's%20IPOs%20send%20positive%20signals%20for%20the%20IPO%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20market%20is%20pretty%20robust.%20It's%20not%20going%20to%20be%20for%20all%20companies%2C%20but%20conditions%20feel%20as%20strong%20as%20I've%20seen%20them%20in%20a%20while%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%209%20healthcare%20startups%20that%20could%20be%20knocking%20on%20the%20IPO%20door%20next%2C%20in%20alphabetical%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAledade%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224480%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Farzad%20Mostashari%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67cf3452b8b41a9673fa318b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223360%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAledade%20CEO%20Dr.%20Farzad%20Mostashari.%3Cp%3ETom%20Sandner%20for%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHealthcare%20startup%20Aledade%20could%20be%20an%20important%20proof%20point%20for%20the%20public%20markets%20on%20the%20viability%20of%20value-based%20care%20enablement%20technologies%2C%20bankers%20and%20investors%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFounded%20in%202014%20by%20former%20national%20coordinator%20for%20health%20IT%20Dr.%20Farzad%20Mostashari%2C%20Aledade%20sells%20data-driven%20software%20to%20independent%20primary%20care%20practices%20to%20help%20them%20deliver%20value-based%20care%2C%20improving%20patient%20outcomes%20while%20lowering%20costs.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20company%20has%20steadily%20grown%20its%20presence%20across%20Medicare%2C%20Medicaid%2C%20and%20commercial%20insurance%20programs%2C%20now%20working%20with%20