Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDatavant%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222832%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kyle%20Armbrester.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67bcd92ec040bd1b4ca2fe31%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222124%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKyle%20Armbrester%2C%20CEO%20of%20Datavant.%3Cp%3EDatavant%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHealth%20data%20startup%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-unicorn-datavant-looking-for-healthcare-acquisition-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDatavant%20has%20been%20deal%20hunting%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20year%2C%20and%20its%20acquisition%20spree%20could%20hint%20at%20a%20coming%20IPO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDatavant%2C%20which%20manages%20patient%20data%20exchanges%20between%20providers%2C%20payers%2C%20and%20life%20sciences%20organizations%2C%20spun%20out%20of%20Vivek%20Ramaswamy's%20Roivant%20Sciences%20in%202017.%20Datavant%20last%20shared%20its%20valuation%20when%20it%20merged%20with%20Ciox%20Health%20in%20June%202021%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nasdaq.com%2Farticles%2Fhealth-data-firms-datavant-ciox-to-merge-in-%247-billion-deal-2021-06-09%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%247%20billion%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20deal%2C%20giving%20it%20the%20highest%20valuation%20of%20the%20startups%20on%20this%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20year%2C%20Datavant%20has%20made%20four%20acquisitions%2C%20most%20recently%20buying%20health%20records%20retrieval%20company%20Ontellus%20in%20June.%20Datavant%20previous%20acquired%20venture-backed%20real-world-evidence%20startup%20Aetion%20in%20May%2C%20and%20picked%20up%20data%20privacy%20organization%20Trace%20Data%20and%20two%20data%20analytics%20products%20from%20healthcare%20AI%20startup%20Apixio%20in%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrivate%20equity%20firm%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-mountain-capital-bringing-big-exits-back-hea