y%20and%20Zoom%2C%20aiming%20to%20help%20clients%20save%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20in%20healthcare%20claims%20with%20its%20evidence-based%20treatment.%20Newly%20public%20Hinge%20Health%20and%20Omada%20Health%20also%20contract%20with%20employers%20with%20similar%20cost-cutting%20aims%2C%20and%20their%20public%20market%20debuts%20could%20bring%20Lyra's%20IPO%20prospects%20into%20focus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20December%2C%20Lyra%20Health%20said%20its%20cofounder%2C%20David%20Ebersman%2C%20would%20transition%20from%20the%20role%20of%20CEO%20to%20board%20chairman%20following%20the%20death%20of%20his%20son%20in%202024.%20Jennifer%20Schulz%2C%20most%20recently%20the%20CEO%20of%20Experian's%20North%20American%20division%2C%20joined%20Lyra%20as%20its%20new%20CEO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBankers%20said%20Schulz's%20experience%20in%20a%20leadership%20role%20at%20publicly%20traded%20Experian%20could%20be%20a%20boon%20to%20Lyra%2C%20though%20the%20startup%20may%20wait%20until%20she's%20further%20settled%20in%20the%20role%20to%20accelerate%20IPO%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELyra%20has%20raised%20more%20than%20%24900%20million%20in%20funding%20to%20date%20from%20investors%20including%20Dragoneer%2C%20Coatue%2C%20and%20Salesforce%20Ventures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELyra%20declined%20to%20comment%20for%20this%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMedline%3Cp%3EMedline%20is%20a%20long-standing%20healthcare%20company%2C%20not%20a%20startup.%20But%20its%20IPO%20could%20make%20waves%20across%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMedline%20was%20founded%20in%201966%20to%20manufacture%20and%20sell%20medical%20supplies%20to%20hospitals%20and%20clinics.%20In%20December%2C%20it%20said%20it%20had%20confidentially%20filed%20its%20S-1%20to%20go%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBankers%20told%20BI%20that%20Medline's%20IPO%20would%20be%20an%20important%20example%20for%20the%20markets%20of%20private%20equity%20buying%20a%20healthcare%20company%20and%20taking%20it%20public%20at%20a%20premium.%20Blackstone%2C%20Carlyle%2C%20and%2