rget%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETranscarent%3C%2Fa%3E%20contracts%20with%20employers%20to%20provide%20health%20navigation%20and%20virtual%20care%20to%20employees.%20The%20startup%20looks%20a%20lot%20closer%20to%20an%20exit%20after%20a%20big%20acquisition%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20bought%20the%20public%20health%20benefits%20company%20Accolade%20in%20a%20%24621%20million%20deal%20that%20closed%20in%20April.%20The%20acquisition%20looks%20to%20have%20significantly%20increased%20Transcarent's%20customer%20base%20and%20thus%20made%20a%20big%20contribution%20to%20its%20top%20line%20%E2%80%94%20before%20the%20Transcarent%20deal%2C%20Accolade%20said%20it%20contracted%20with%20over%201%2C400%20employers%20and%20health%20plans%2C%20and%20the%20company%20reported%20%24414%20million%20in%20revenue%20in%20the%20fiscal%20year%202024.%20Now%2C%20with%20Accolade%20on%20board%2C%20Transcarent%20says%20it%20works%20with%20over%201%2C700%20employers%20and%20health%20plans.%20Transcarent%20hasn't%20publicly%20shared%20its%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Accolade%20acquisition%20was%20financed%20by%20Transcarent%20investors%20including%20General%20Catalyst%20and%20CEO%20Glen%20Tullman's%2062%20Ventures%2C%20cash%20on%20Transcarent's%20balance%20sheet%2C%20and%20debt%20provided%20by%20JP%20Morgan.%20Transcarent%20has%20raised%20about%20%24450%20million%20since%20its%202020%20founding%2C%20including%20%24126%20million%20in%20a%20Series%20D%20funding%20round%20in%20May%202024%20at%20a%20%242.2%20billion%20valuation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETullman%20has%20by%20far%20the%20most%20experience%20with%20taking%20companies%20public%20of%20the%20CEOs%20on%20this%20list.%20Before%20Transcarent%2C%20he%20led%20three%20companies%20through%20public%20listings%20%E2%80%94%20Livongo%2C%20Allscripts%2C%20and%20Enterprise%20Systems.%20His%20success%20with%20Livongo%2C%20the%20diabetes%20care%20company%20he%20founded%2C%20stands%20out%20as%20a%20rare%20example%20of%20blockbuster%20digital%20health%20returns%3B%20Livongo%20went%20public%20in%202019%20at%20a%20%242.5%20billion%20valuation%2C%20before%20being%20acquired%20by%20Teladoc%20the%20next%20year%20for%20%2418.5%20billion%2C%20at%20the%20time%20the%20biggest%20deal%20ever%20in%20the%20digital%20health%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20experience%20could%20set%20Transcarent%20up%20to%20pursue%20an%20IPO%20when%20market%20conditions%20look%20favorable.%20Tullman%20told%20MedCity%20News%20in%20May%202024%20that%20he%20had%20%26quot%3Bno%20interest%26quot%3B%20in%20selling%20the%20company%2C%20but%20would%20consider%20an%20IPO%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETranscarent%20will%20have%20to%20separate%20itself%20from%20previous%20care%20navigation%20IPOs%2C%20however%2C%20including%20Health%20Catalyst%2C%20whose%20stock%20has%20declined%20more%20than%2085%25%20since%20its%202019%20IPO.%20It'll%20also%20need%20to%20contend%20with%20Accolade's%20cash%20burn%2C%20since%20the%20health%20benefits%20company%20reported%20a%20net%20loss%20of%20%24100%20million%20in%20the%20fiscal%20year%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20to%20BI%2C%20Tullman%20said%20Transcarent%20is%20focused%20on%20integrating%20its%20solutions%20to%20bring%20its%20AI-powered%20platform%2C%20called%20WayFinding%2C%20to%20more%20members%20and%20employers%20to%20make%20healthcare%20more%20accessible%20and%20affordable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20Transcarent%2C%20our%20priority%20is%20meeting%20the%20needs%20of%20our%20Members%20and%20delivering%20measurable%20results%20for%20our%20clients.%20If%20we%20do%20those%20things%20well%2C%20the%20rest%20will%20follow%2C%26quot%3B%20Tullman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EVirta%20Health%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sami%20Inkinen%2C%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Virta%20Health.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685d95e085e81483682cd912%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22750%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESami%20Inkinen%2C%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Virta%20Health.%3Cp%3EVirta%20Health%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOmada%20Health's%20June%20IPO%20could%20set%20up%20diabetes%20care%20peer%20Virta%20Health%20to%20follow%20in%20its%20footsteps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFounded%20in%202014%2C%20Virta%20Health%20made%20its%20name%20in%20virtual%20diabetes%20care%2C%20helping%20patients%20reverse%20type%202%20diabetes%20through%20personalized%2C%20low-carb%20nutrition%20plans.%20It's%20expanding%20quickly%20into%20obesity%20treatment%20and%20added%20GLP-1%20prescriptions%20like%20Ozempic%20for%20weight%20loss%20in%20January.%20The%20company%20previously%20prescribed%20GLP-1s%20only%20for%20diabetes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECEO%20Sami%20Inkinen%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20January%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvirta-health-prescribing-ozempic-profitability-ipo-diabetes-startup-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EVirta%20was%20bringing%20in%20over%20%24100%20million%20in%20annual%20recurring%20revenue%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20up%2060%25%20from%20the%20year%20before.%20He%20said%20he%20expected%20even%20faster%20growth%20in%202025%2C%20driven%20by%20surging%20demand%20for%20Virta's%20weight-loss%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20IPO%20is%20the%20next%20milestone%20for%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Inkinen%20said%20at%20the%20time.%20He%20declined%20to%20provide%20details%20on%20Virta's%20potential%20IPO%20timing%2C%20but%20said%20the%20company%20wants%20to%20be%20profitable%20before%20it%20braves%20the%20public%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVirta%20was%20last%20valued%20at%20%242%20billion%20in%202021%2C%20when%20it%20raised%20%24133%20million%20in%20Series%20E%20funding%20led%20by%20Tiger%20Global.%20Inkinen%20said%20in%20January%20that%20Virta%20would%20be%20profitable%20by%20the%20end%20of%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20conversation%20with%20BI%20at%20the%20end%20of%20June%2C%20Inkinen%20declined%20to%20share%20specifics%20about%20a%20potential%20Virta%20IPO%20or%20a%20likely%20timeline%20for%20its%20public%20listing.%20However%2C%20he%20said%20it's%20always%20been%20his%20plan%20for%20Virta%20to%20be%20an%20independent%20public%20company%2C%20adding%20that%20Virta%20is%20tracking%20towards%20that%20goal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInkinen%20said%20Virta's%20growth%20rate%20is%20accelerating%20and%20that%20the%20company%20is%20ahead%20of%20its%20financial%20targets%20for%20the%20year.%20He's%20not%20stressing%20about%20timing%20the%20market%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20very%20best%20investor%20relations%20is%20fantastic%20financials.%20If%20you%20have%20those%20as%20a%20company%2C%20that's%20the%20best%20marketing%20before%20IPO%2C%20and%20for%20the%20IPO%20and%20beyond.%20Build%20a%20great%20business%2C%20and%20the%20rest%20will%20take%20care%20of%20itself%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EZelis%3Cp%3EZelis%20was%20started%2030%20years%20ago%20under%20the%20name%20Stratose%2C%20later%20merging%20with%20GlobalCare%20and%20Pay-Plus%20Solutions%20to%20create%20Zelis%20Healthcare.%20The%20company%20now%20sells%20healthtech%20software%20to%20payers%20and%20providers%20to%20manage%20medical%20claims%20and%20process%20electronic%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBankers%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20Zelis's%20business%20is%20stable%20with%20strong%20economics%20that%20could%20position%20it%20well%20for%20an%20IPO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZelis's%20profile%20isn't%20too%20dissimilar%20from%20Waystar%2C%20a%20private-equity-backed%20healthcare%20payments%20company%20that%20went%20public%20in%20June%202024%20with%20an%20initial%20market%20cap%20of%20about%20%243.5%20billion.%20Since%20then%2C%20Waystar's%20stock%20has%20risen%20about%2088%25%2C%20and%20as%20of%20late%20June%2C%20the%20company%20boasts%20a%20%246.7%20billion%20market%20cap.%20That%20success%20could%20set%20Zelis%20up%20to%20follow%20in%20Waystar's%20footsteps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZelis%20announced%20it%20had%20sold%20a%20minority%20stake%20for%20an%20undisclosed%20price%20in%20December%2C%20led%20by%20Mubadala%20Capital%20and%20including%20Norwest%20and%20HarbourVest.%20The%20recent%20capital%20raise%20could%20push%20Zelis's%20IPO%20back%20if%20the%20company%20doesn't%20see%20a%20significant%20financial%20benefit%20to%20going%20public%2C%20bankers%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZelis%20declined%20to%20comment%20for%20this%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhealthcare-startups-in-line-go-public-according-to-bankers-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1751878801000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686429cd3d5881a51c1c77b2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhealthcare-startups-in-line-go-public-according-to-bankers-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20digital%20health%20market%20is%20welcoming%20new%20IPOs%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20years.%20Bankers%20and%20investors%20think%20these%209%20startups%20could%20go%20public%20next.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rtorrence%40businessinsider.com%20(Rebecca%20Torrence)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhealthcare-startups-in-line-go-public-according-to-bankers-2025-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Musk%20posts%20'arrest%20counter'%20of%20Epstein%20case%3B%20fresh%20dig%20at%20Trump%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1751878778000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-122294742%2Cimgsize-1155728.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fwhats-the-time-oh-look-musk-posts-arrest-counter-of-epstein-case-space-x-ceos-fresh-dig-at-trump%2Farticleshow%2F122294035.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk%20posted%20an%20%26quot%3Barrest%20counter%26quot%3B%20on%2