y.%20I'm%20not%20foolish%20enough%20to%20call%20this%20a%20bubble%2C%20and%20I%20think%20AI%20will%20eventually%20deliver%20benefits%20for%20our%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20not%20there%20yet%2C%20though%2C%20even%20though%20investors%20like%20to%20think%20so.%20It%20takes%20years%20for%20big%20technological%20trends%20to%20take%20hold%2C%20and%20productivity%20usually%20shines%20through%20when%20workers%20feel%20empowered%20and%20companies%20feel%20comfortable%20expanding.%20That's%20far%20from%20the%20case%20right%20now%20%E2%80%94%20business%20confidence%20is%20in%20the%20dumps%2C%20so%20we're%20in%20the%20opposite%20scenario.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20economy%20is%20getting%20weaker%2C%20it's%20best%20to%20grasp%20onto%20what's%20real%20in%20your%20portfolio.%20And%20there's%20a%20striking%20gap%20between%20AI%20and%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ECallie%20Cox%20is%20the%20chief%20market%20strategist%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ritholtzwealth.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3ERitholtz%20Wealth%20Management%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20and%20the%20author%20of%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.optimisticallie.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3EOptimistiCallie%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20a%20newsletter%20of%20Wall%20Street-quality%20research%20for%20everyday%20investors.%20You%20can%20view%20Ritholtz's%20disclosures%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ritholtzwealth.com%2Fblog-disclosures%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ehere%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmassive-ai-investment-slowing-economy-recession-stock-market-crash-earnings-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insi