yan%20Trostle%2FGoogle%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ELogan%20Kilpatrick%20is%20Google's%20head%20of%20developer%20relations%20and%20runs%20the%20company's%20AI%20Studio.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe's%20also%20become%20a%20one-man%20marketing%20machine%2C%20regularly%20hyping%20up%20Google's%20AI%20products%20on%20X.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGoogle%20has%20sometimes%20struggled%20to%20get%20credit%20in%20the%20AI%20race%2C%20but%20Kilpatrick%20told%20BI%20he's%20keen%20to%20change%20that%20narrative.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20not%20an%20executive%2C%20a%20company%20spokesperson%2C%20or%20a%20world-class%20researcher.%20But%20he%20might%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprotesters-accuse-google-deepmind-breaking-promises-ai-safety-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGoogle's%3C%2Fa%3E%20secret%20weapon%20in%20winning%20the%20AI%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20an%20AI%20developer%2C%20you've%20likely%20heard%20of%20Logan%20Kilpatrick.%20As%20Google's%20head%20of%20developer%20relations%2C%20Kilpatrick%2C%2027%2C%20runs%20AI%20Studio%2C%20the%20company's%20AI%20developer%20software%20program.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20also%20become%20Google's%20delegate%20for%20speaking%20to%20the%20AI%20community%20and%20%E2%80%94%20intentionally%20or%20not%20%E2%80%94%20a%20one-man%20marketing%20machine%20for%20the%20company's%20AI%20products.%20He's%20a%20prolific%20poster%20on%20X%2C%20where%20he'll%20sometimes%20hype%20Google's%20latest%20Gemini%20releases%20or%20tease%20something%20new%20on%20the%20horizon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbove%20all%2C%20he%20is%20one%20of%20the%20people%20tasked%20with%20translating%20Google's%20AI%20breakthroughs%20to%20the%20global%20developer%20community.%20It's%20a%20crucial%20job%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20search%20giant%20needs%20to%20not%20just%20convince%20developers%20to%20use%20its%20products%2C%20but%20capture%20a%20new%20generation%20of%20builders%20entering%20the%20fray%20as%20AI%20makes%20it%20easier%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvibe-coding-software-engineer-skills-jobs-ai-cursor-chatgpt-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eanyone%20to%20make%20software%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20want%20AI%20to%20have%20the%20level%20of%20impact%20on%20humanity%20that%20I%20think%20it%20could%20have%2C%20you%20need%20to%20be%20able%20to%20provide%20a%20platform%20for%20developers%20in%20order%20to%20go%20and%20do%20this%20stuff%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20an%20interview.%20%26quot%3BThe%20reality%20is%20there's%20a%20thousand%20and%20one%20things%20that%20Google%20is%20never%20going%20to%20build%2C%20and%20doesn't%20make%20sense%20for%20us%20to%20build%2C%20that%20developers%20want%20to%20build.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompany%20insiders%20say%20Google%20has%20recognized%20Kilpatrick's%20strength%20and%20given%20him%20more%20responsibilities%20and%20visibility.%20He%20could%20be%20seen%20onstage%20at%20this%20year's%20Google%20I%2FO%20conference%20and%20even%20had%20a%20fireside%20chat%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Do7U4DV9Fkc0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewith%20Google%20cofounder%20Sergey%20Brin%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20really%20crave%20legitimacy%2C%20authenticity%2C%20and%20competency%2C%20and%20Logan%20combines%20all%20three%2C%26quot%3B%20Asara%20Near%2C%20a%20startup%20founder%20who%20has%20occasionally%20contacted%20Kilpatrick%20with%20development%20questions%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2230e74dc2-d015-4f91-9abe-61142e479407%5C%22%3ELoganGPT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20OpenAI%20was%20preparing%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-ai-chaos-openia-google-creatives-academics-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elaunch%20ChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20fire%20the%20starting%20gun%20on%20one%20of%20history's%20most%20profound%20technological%20shifts.%20Kilpatrick%2C%20who%20has%20a%20technical%20background%20and%20worked%20at%20Apple%20and%20NASA%2C%20saw%20an%20online%20job%20ad%20for%20OpenAI%20and%20was%20soon%20facing%20a%20tricky%20decision%3A%20to%20work%20at%20what%20was%20then%20Sam%20Altman's%20little-known%20startup%2C%20or%20take%20a%20gig%20at%20IBM.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20decided%20that%20OpenAI%20was%20worth%20a%20shot%20%E2%80%94%20and%20within%20a%20few%20months%2C%20found%20himself%20at%20the%20center%20of%20the%20biggest%20tech%20launch%20since%20the%20debut%20of%20the%20iPhone%20in%202007.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20OpenAI%20experience%20was%20a%20startup%20experience%20for%20about%20six%20months%20and%20then%20it%20became%20basically%20a%20hyperscaler%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI.%20It%20was%20chaotic%2C%20but%20it%20helped%20Kilpatrick%20learn%20how%20to%20build%20an%20ecosystem%20and%20cut%20his%20teeth%20as%20the%20developers'%20go-to%20guy.%20There%2C%20developers%20nicknamed%20him%20%26quot%3BLoganGPT.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224240%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Logan%20Kilpatrick%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6867f6f93d5881a51c1cbbda%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222384%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKilpatrick%20joined%20OpenAI%20months%20before%20the%20public%20launch%20of%20ChatGPT.%20%3Cp%3EBrett%20A.%20Sims%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20left%20OpenAI%20in%202024%20for%20Google%2C%20developers%20and%20peers%20made%20clear%20it%20was%20a%20huge%20loss%20for%20the%20ChatGPT%20maker%2C%20and%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-ai-talent-war-big-win-logan-kilpatrick-openai-developers-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebig%20win%20for%20Google%20in%20the%20AI%20talent%20transfer%20window%3C%2Fa%3E.%20AI%20Studio%20was%20then%20still%20a%20project%20inside%20Google's%20Labs%20division%2C%20and%20Kilpatrick%20and%20his%20team%20were%20tasked%20with%20migrating%20it%20into%20a%20fully-fledged%20product%20inside%20Google's%20Cloud%20unit.%20It%20was%20again%20like%20going%20from%20zero%20to%20one%3A%20AI%20Studio%20was%20pre-revenue%20with%20no%20customers%2C%20but%20with%20a%20long%20tail%20of%20developers%20ready%20to%20jump%20on%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20felt%20oddly%20almost%20like%20the%20same%20exact%20experience%20I've%20lived%20through%20at%20two%20different%20companies%20and%20two%20different%20cultures%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20May%20this%20year%2C%20Kilpatrick%20was%20promoted%2C%20and%20his%20team%20running%20AI%20Studio%20was%20moved%20from%20the%20Cloud%20unit%20to%20Google%20DeepMind%2C%20bringing%20them%20closer%20to%20the%20researchers%20working%20on%20the%20underlying%20models%20and%20the%20employees%20working%20on%20its%20Gemini%20chatbot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20kind%20of%20all%20over%20the%20place%2C%20and%20that's%20his%20superpower%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20one%20senior%20employee%20who%20requested%20anonymity%20because%20they%20were%20not%20permitted%20to%20speak%20to%20the%20media.%20They%20said%20that%20Google%20has%20put%20Kilpatrick%20in%20charge%20of%20more%20products%20as%20leaders%20have%20recognized%20his%20ability%20to%20engage%20so%20effectively%20with%20the%20developer%20community.%20%26quot%3BLogan%20is%2090%25%20of%20Google's%20marketing%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b9dba05f-0375-42a4-82b1-debb86d6cc88%5C%22%3EHelping%20Google%20win%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20paper%2C%20Google%20is%20an%20AI%20winner.%20The%20reality%20is%20more%20complicated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20latest%20Gemini%202.0%20Pro%20model%20ranks%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhuggingface.co%2Fspaces%2Flmarena-ai%2Fchatbot-arena-leaderboard%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etop%20of%20multiple%20leaderboards%3C%2Fa%3E%20across%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flmarena.ai%2Fleaderboard%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erange%20of%20testing%20areas%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20this%20hasn't%20always%20been%20reflected%20in%20the%20number%20of%20users.%20Google's%20CEO%2C%20Sundar%20Pichai%2C%20said%20in%20May%20that%20the%20company's%20Gemini%20app%20has%20more%20than%20400%20million%20%3Cem%3Emonthly%3C%2Fem%3E%20active%20users.%20That's%20well%20behind%20the%20500%20million%20%3Cem%3Eweekly%3C%2Fem%3E%20active%20users%20for%20ChatGPT%2C%20according%20to%20figures%20shared%20by%20Altman%20in%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDeepMind%20doesn't%20get%20nearly%20as%20much%20credit%20and%20attention%20as%20they%20deserve%2C%20and%20that's%20because%20comms%20is%20vastly%20underperforming%20capabilities%2C%26quot%3B%20communications%20executive%20Lulu%20Meservey%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Flulumeservey%2Fstatus%2F1922277064045998189%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eposted%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20May.%20Responding%20to%20another%20person%2C%20she%20wrote%3A%20%26quot%3BLogan%20is%20like%2090%25%20of%20their%20comms.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20struggle%2C%20insiders%20say%2C%20is%20due%20to%20Google%20owning%20multiple%20products%20that%20aren't%20always%20clearly%20distinct.%20Developers%20can%20build%20using%20Vertex%20in%20Google%20Cloud%20or%20AI%20Studio.%20Meanwhile%20Google%20has%20a%20consumer-facing%20app%20simply%20called%20Gemini.%20The%20same%20models%20aren't%20necessarily%20always%20available%20across%20all%20three%20places%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcreatoreconomy.so%2Fp%2Fwhy-are-googles-ai-products-so-frustrating%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhich%20can%20get%20confusing%20for%20users%20and%20developers%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20the%20problem%20of%20being%20a%20quarter-century-old%20tech%20behemoth%20with%20more%20nimble%20startups%20nipping%20at%20its%20heels.%20%26quot%3BOpenAI%20can%20put%20all%20their%20messaging%20arrows%20behind%20one%20thing%2C%20while%20Google%20has%20messaging%20arrows%20behind%2010%2C000%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20former%20Google%20product%20manager%20Rajat%20Paharia%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Logan%20Kilpatrick%20speaks%20at%20Google%20IO%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6867f7703d5881a51c1cbbe1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELogan%20Kilpatrick%20speaking%20at%20Google%20I%2FO.%3Cp%3EGoogle%2FRyan%20Trostle%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EKilpatrick%20recognizes%20that%20Google%20has%20work%20to%20do.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20Google%20on%20a%20net%20basis%20is%20doing%20so%20much%20in%20the%20world%20right%20now%2C%20and%20AI%20is%20around%20everything%20that%20we're%20doing%2C%20and%20I%20think%20a%20lot%20of%20narrative%20doesn't%20capture%20innovation%20is%20happening%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20big%20part%20of%20Kilpatrick's%20job%20is%20trying%20to%20cement%20that%20narrative%20among%20the%20global%20developer%20base.%20At%20OpenAI%2C%20Sam%20Altman's%20Jobsian%20showmanship%20has%20made%20him%20a%20highly%20effective%20salesman%20both%20for%20his%20company's%20products%20and%20his%20vision%20for%20the%20future%20of%20this%20technology.%20Or%2C%20as%20Paharia%20described%20Altman%20to%20BI%2C%20a%20%26quot%3Bshowman%20with%20rizz.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20may%20have%20found%20its%20equivalent%20in%20Kilpatrick.%20He%20told%20BI%20that%20he%20often%20posts%20on%20X%20because%20it%20has%20become%20something%20of%20a%20town%20square%20for%20AI%20developers%20and%20enthusiasts%2C%20all%20champing%20at%20the%20bit%20for%20the%20latest%20crumb%20of%20news.%20It's%20a%20community%20filled%20with%20hype%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fnatolambert%2Fstatus%2F1909612007634145464%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20%26quot%3Bvagueposting%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20steeped%20deeply%20in%20lore%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.latent.space%2Fp%2Fwhat-ilya-saw%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhat%20did%20Ilya%20see%3F%3C%2Fa%3E).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20day%20that%20OpenAI's%20latest%20release%20sucking%20is%20grabbing%20everyone's%20attention%2C%20Kilpatrick%20may%20log%20on%20and%20post%20a%20single%20word%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3BGemini%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20just%20to%20rev%20the%20hype%20engine%20a%20little.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKilpatrick%20often%20has%20%26quot%3Ba%20thousand%26quot%3B%20emails%20from%20developers%20that%20need%20responding%20to%2C%20he%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BI%20spend%20probably%20as%20much%20time%20as%20I%20physically%20can%20responding%20to%20stuff%20these%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20And%20that's%20between%20the%20numerous%20product%20meetings%20(he%20had%2022%20meetings%20scheduled%20on%20the%20day%20we%20spoke%20in%20early%20July%2C%2023%20the%20day%20before).%20He%20once%20posted%20on%20X%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20online%207%20days%20a%20week%2C%20~8%2B%20hours%20a%20day.%20If%20you%20need%20something%20as%20you%20build%20with%20Gemini%2C%20please%20ping%20me!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDevelopers%20say%20they%20like%20that%20Kilpatrick%20takes%20the%20time%20to%20engage%20and%20listen%20to%20their%20feedback.%20%26quot%3BThe%20few%20times%20I've%20emailed%20him%20to%20get%20help%20with%20something%2C%20they%20near-instantly%20responded%20and%20helped%20resolve%20the%20issue%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Near%2C%20the%20startup%20founder.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20opposite%20of%20my%20experience%20through%20normal%20support%20channels.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAndrew%20Curran%2C%20an%20AI%20commentator%20who%20frequently%20posts%20to%20X%2C%20wrote%20last%20month%20that%20Kilpatrick%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Ban%20incredible%20hire%26quot%3B%20for%20Google.%20%26quot%3BTo%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20he%20is%20now%20the%20face%20of%20Gemini%2C%20I%20bet%20most%20people%20don't%20even%20remember%20his%20OAI%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FAndrewCurran_%2Fstatus%2F1938014033858474227%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehe%20wrote.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKilpatrick%20told%20BI%20that%20because%20he%20is%20a%20developer%20himself%2C%20he%20finds%20it%20easy%20to%20understand%20the%20core%20target%20user.%20He%20said%20this%20has%20helped%20in%20building%20out%20Google's%20AI%20Studio%2C%20and%20that%20engaging%20with%20developers%20comes%20naturally.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20the%20obvious%20thing%20to%20do%20if%20you%20want%20to%20build%20a%20product%20for%20developers%2C%20is%20like%2C%20go%20talk%20to%20your%20users%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22twitter%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHe's%20been%20an%20incredible%20hire%20for%20Google.%20To%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20he%20is%20now%20the%20face%20of%20Gemini%2C%20I%20bet%20most%20people%20don't%20even%20remember%20his%20OAI%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Andrew%20Curran%20(%40AndrewCurran_)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAndrewCurran_%2Fstatus%2F1938014033858474227%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJune%2025%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20definition%20of%20developer%20is%20changing%20with%20approaches%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvibe-coding-ai-silicon-valley-andrej-karpathy-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evibe%20coding%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20lets%20non-technical%20people%20create%20software%20by%20describing%20what%20they'd%20like%20to%20an%20AI%20tool.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20it%20means%20to%20be%20a%20developer%20right%20now%20looks%20a%20little%20different%20than%20it%20did%20two%20years%20ago%20or%20three%2