%20and%20divorce%20%E2%80%94%20these%20early%20Indian%20laws%20gave%20women%20power%20in%20a%20time%20when%20society%20barely%20gave%20them%20a%20voice.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Srimoyee%20Chowdhury%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F461335%2Fearly-indian-feminist-laws%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Pocket-Sized%20Device%20Can%20Test%20Your%20Soil%20in%205%20Minutes%3B%20Here%E2%80%99s%20How%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFor%20generations%2C%20Indian%20farmers%20have%20relied%20on%20traditional%20wisdom%20and%20visual%20cues%20to%20care%20for%20their%20land.%20Decades%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F324349%2Fmaharashtra-agriculture-entomologist-sangita-sawalakhe-vidarbha-biotech-biopesticides-biofertilisers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoveruse%20of%20chemical%20fertilisers%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20left%20the%20soil%20exhausted%20and%20less%20productive.%20About%20fifty%20years%20ago%2C%20producing%20two%20tonnes%20of%20crops%20per%20hectare%20required%20just%2054%20kilograms%20of%20fertiliser.%20Today%2C%20that%20same%20yield%20demands%20over%20280%20kilograms%2C%20which%20is%20a%20startling%20sign%20that%20the%20soil%20is%20no%20longer%20responding%20the%20way%20it%20once%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFertilisers%20are%20added%20without%20knowing%20what%20the%20soil%20needs.%20And%20while%20soil%20testing%20could%20solve%20this%2C%20the%20reality%20is%20that%20it%20is%20slow%2C%20inconvenient%2C%20and%20often%20too%20expensive.%20Farmers%20must%20collect%20half%20a%20kilo%20of%20soil%2C%20send%20it%20to%20a%20distant%20lab%2C%20and%20then%20wait%2010%20to%2015%20days%2C%20by%20which%20time%20seeds%20have%20already%20been%20sown%2C%20and%20fertilisers%20have%20already%20been%20spread.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20significant%20breakthrough%20has%20finally%20provided%20a%20solution%20t